## Appendix: Notation Summary

| Symbol | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| $\mathbf{x}$ | Input activation |
| $\mathbf{z}$ | Sparse latent code |
| $\hat{\mathbf{x}}$ | Reconstructed activation |
| $d$ | Input dimension |
| $m$ | Latent dimension ($m = k \cdot d$) |
| $k$ | Expansion factor |
| $W_{\text{enc}}$ | Encoder weights |
| $W_{\text{dec}}$ | Decoder weights ($= W_{\text{enc}}^T$) |
| $\lambda$ | L₁ sparsity coefficient |
| $R^2$ | Coefficient of determination |
| $L_0$ | Number of active features |
| $f_{\text{dead}}$ | Dead feature fraction |
| $\alpha$ | Learning rate |
| $B$ | Batch size |
| $T_{\text{max}}$ | Maximum training steps |

